          "id": "e74abf5fe235455f88b4df4cd261a9eff73bc655",
          "message": "[fix][acc] fix accuracy of fp8 attn weights model using ptpc quant recipe (#670)\n\n* correct the quant type based on recipe for fuse_qknorm_quant\n\n* remove debug print\n\n* use quant type\n\nSigned-off-by: zejunchen-zejun <zejun.chen@amd.com>\n\n* use unified aiter fused_qk_norm interface\n\nSigned-off-by: zejunchen-zejun <zejun.chen@amd.com>\n\n* change the import path for fused_qknorm\n\nSigned-off-by: zejunchen-zejun <zejun.chen@amd.com>\n\n* fix qknorm quant compile path\n\n* document qknorm quant compile guard\n\n* simplify qknorm quant dispatch\n\n* use single rmsnorm quant entrypoint\n\n* update api\n\n* clean the qk rmsnorm code\n\n* fix corner case\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: zejunchen-zejun <zejun.chen@amd.com>\nCo-authored-by: Guanbao Yu <gyu@amd.com>\nCo-authored-by: zejunchen-zejun <zejun.chen@amd.com>\nCo-authored-by: wuhuikx <hattie.wu@amd.com>\nCo-authored-by: XiaobingSuper <xiaobingzhangupc@gmail.com>",
